(Nr. 7a)
</td>
</tr>
<tr id="E10145A20AA8AF0C2167DC02D974A4A4" pageId="null" pageNumber="601">
<td id="F1E3BEB65815A421A5EC6D84AF9EEB2C" align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="601" valign="top">
1*. Pflanze kahl oder zerstreut behaart; Kelch 5-9 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken id="2890AF5D80E767879553FE38906E2558" originalValue="längere" pageId="null" pageNumber="601">laengere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="4E73064D766A7F9B297B4E8EB9F8C83F" originalValue="Kelchzähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="601">Kelchzaehne</normalizedToken>
